      • merge

        public static <T> T merge(String jsonBase,
          String jsonNew,
          Class<T> clazz)
        Merge two json packages into one class. Note: This does not do a deep merge!
        Type Parameters:
        T - a T object.
        Parameters:
        jsonBase - The base json. This forms the base of the object.
        jsonNew - The new json to add to the object, this will override the data from jsonBase.
        clazz - The class to convert too.
        Returns:
        The new merged object.
